me here today is--

00:00:06.350 --> 00:00:07.780
ADAM KOCH: Hi guys, Adam Koch.

00:00:07.780 --> 00:00:08.740
And over in London--

00:00:08.740 --> 00:00:10.680
NICK BUTCHER: Hi,
Nick Butcher.

00:00:10.680 --> 00:00:14.870
ROMAN NURIK: So today, unlike
most days on the show--

00:00:14.870 --> 00:00:17.190
