that have been nominated--

00:00:25.990 --> 00:00:28.540
usually the developer nominates
themselves--

00:00:28.540 --> 00:00:31.560
and take a look at how we can
reimagine some of the screens

00:00:31.560 --> 00:00:36.950
in those apps to fit better with
