at that certain size.

00:09:50.270 --> 00:09:51.090
And then--

00:09:51.090 --> 00:09:52.810
ROMAN NURIK: And it looks
like-- sorry, Nick--

00:09:52.810 --> 00:09:55.250
it looks like on a tablet,
they have just a slightly

00:09:55.250 --> 00:09:56.245
wider margin.

00:09:56.245 --> 00:09:59.350
I don't know if it's an
increment of 16 DIPs, like we

00:09:59.350 --> 00:10:01.620
talked about, but it's
definitely noticeably larger

00:10:01.620 --> 00:10:04.136
to the left and to the right
of the patterns.

00:10:04.136 --> 00:10:05.670
NICK BUTCHER: Yeah, and then
just last thing I can say,

00:10:05.670 --> 00:10:07.910
when you step out from the 7-
to the 10-inch and have even

00:10:07.910 --> 00:10:10.800
