potential wallpapers

00:10:13.820 --> 00:10:15.290
on screen at once.

00:10:15.290 --> 00:10:19.350
So it's kind of reimagining
the content, the

00:10:19.350 --> 00:10:20.480
representation of the content.

00:10:20.480 --> 00:10:22.220
So it's the same content but
laid out in a completely

00:10:22.220 --> 00:10:26.416
different way to just make much
better use of the space.

00:10:26.416 --> 00:10:29.500
ROMAN NURIK: Yeah, and I just
