00:19:56.980 --> 00:20:00.750
And here on a tablet that's
10 inches, they're 32 DIP.

00:20:00.750 --> 00:20:04.760
And that actually gives a little
bit more breathing room

00:20:04.760 --> 00:20:07.650
for the content on this
10-inch device.

00:20:07.650 --> 00:20:09.330
And you'll notice this on the
next screen as well, once we

00:20:09.330 --> 00:20:14.400
get to it, that this adds
a sense of spacing and

00:20:14.400 --> 00:20:17.540
separation of the two pieces
of content, or in here, the

00:20:17.540 --> 00:20:20.460
three different pieces
of content.

00:20:20.460 --> 00:20:22.636
Any thoughts, guys?

00:20:22.636 --> 00:20:24.815
NICK BUTCHER: It's
a beautiful app.

00:20:24.815 --> 00:20:27.700
ADAM KOCH: Whoever designed
this is amazing--

