00:24:29.300 --> 00:24:32.850
really just about text length
and white space.

00:24:32.850 --> 00:24:37.860
You really want to optimize to
minimize large, large swaths

00:24:37.860 --> 00:24:40.570
of white space, where there's
just nothing on screen.

00:24:40.570 --> 00:24:43.220
You don't want to throw
information along one of the

00:24:43.220 --> 00:24:45.440
